statements: SELECT * FROM fitness_data WHERE user_id = 1;
SELECT exercise_type, calories_burned FROM fitness_data WHERE duration_minutes > 30;
SELECT user_id, exercise_type, date FROM fitness_data ORDER BY date DESC;
SELECT exercise_type, duration_minutes FROM fitness_data WHERE calories_burned > 200 ORDER BY duration_minutes ASC;
SELECT MAX(calories_burned) AS max_calories_burned FROM fitness_data;
SELECT * FROM fitness_data WHERE user_id = 101 ORDER BY date DESC;
SELECT exercise_type, SUM(duration_minutes) AS total_duration FROM fitness_data GROUP BY exercise_type HAVING total_duration > 30;
SELECT user_id, exercise_type, date FROM fitness_data WHERE calories_burned > 500 AND date BETWEEN '2021-01-01' AND '2021-12-31';
SELECT AVG(calories_burned) AS avg_calories, MAX(duration_minutes) AS max_duration FROM fitness_data WHERE user_id = 201 AND exercise_type = 'Running';
SELECT user_id, COUNT(*) AS total_entries FROM fitness_data GROUP BY user_id HAVING total_entries >= 5 ORDER BY total_entries DESC;
SELECT * FROM fitness_users WHERE user_id = '123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000';
SELECT username, email FROM fitness_users ORDER BY username DESC;
SELECT exercise_name, duration, date FROM exercise_data WHERE calories_burned > 500 ORDER BY date ASC;
SELECT user_id, exercise_name, calories_burned FROM exercise_data WHERE date = '2022-01-15';
SELECT dob, COUNT(*) FROM fitness_users GROUP BY dob HAVING COUNT(*) > 1;
SELECT username, email FROM fitness_users;
SELECT user_id, username, email, dob FROM fitness_users WHERE email LIKE '%gmail.com';
SELECT exercise_name, duration, calories_burned FROM exercise_data WHERE duration > 30;
SELECT user_id, date, exercise_name, duration, calories_burned FROM exercise_data WHERE date >= '2022-01-01' ORDER BY date DESC;
SELECT user_id, username, email, date, exercise_name, duration, calories_burned FROM fitness_users JOIN exercise_data ON fitness_users.user_id = exercise_data.user_id;
SELECT * FROM exercise_data;
SELECT exercise_name, calories_burned FROM exercise_data WHERE exercise_duration > 30;
SELECT user_id, exercise_date FROM exercise_data ORDER BY exercise_date DESC;
SELECT * FROM health_insights WHERE bmi < 25;
SELECT app_name, app_description FROM app_integration WHERE integration_status = TRUE;
SELECT * FROM exercise_data WHERE exercise_name = 'Running' AND calories_burned > 200 ORDER BY exercise_date DESC;

SELECT user_id, exercise_name, exercise_duration, calories_burned FROM exercise_data WHERE exercise_duration >= 30 AND exercise_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-06-30' ORDER BY exercise_duration DESC;

SELECT e.user_id, e.exercise_name, e.exercise_duration, h.bmi FROM exercise_data e JOIN health_insights h ON e.user_id = h.user_id WHERE e.calories_burned > 150 AND h.bmi < 25 ORDER BY e.exercise_date DESC;
SELECT a.app_id, a.app_name, a.app_description, i.heart_rate FROM app_integration a LEFT JOIN health_insights i ON a.app_id = i.user_id WHERE a.integration_status = TRUE AND i.heart_rate > 80;

SELECT e.user_id, e.exercise_name, e.exercise_duration, h.heart_rate, h.health_score FROM exercise_data e INNER JOIN health_insights h ON e.user_id = h.user_id WHERE h.heart_rate < 70 AND h.health_score > 8.0 ORDER BY e.exercise_date ASC;
SELECT * FROM users ORDER BY age DESC;
SELECT username, email FROM users WHERE height > 170;
SELECT user_id, exercise_type, duration_min FROM exercise_logs WHERE calories_burned > 300;
SELECT workout_name, target_duration_min FROM workouts ORDER BY date_added DESC;
SELECT user_id, analysis_date, insights FROM health_insights;
SELECT * FROM users WHERE age > 30 ORDER BY username ASC;
SELECT username, email FROM users WHERE weight > 70;
SELECT workout_name, exercise_type, target_duration_min FROM workouts WHERE date_added > '2022-01-01' ORDER BY target_duration_min DESC;
SELECT user_id, username, email, age, height, weight FROM users WHERE user_id = '123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000';
SELECT insight_id, user_id, analysis_date, insights FROM health_insights WHERE analysis_date BETWEEN '2021-01-01' AND '2022-01-01' ORDER BY analysis_date DESC;
SELECT * FROM exercise_data WHERE user_id = 1;
SELECT exercise_name, calories_burned, date FROM exercise_data WHERE duration_minutes > 30;
SELECT user_id, weight_kg, bmi FROM health_insights WHERE bmi >= 25;
SELECT * FROM workout_schedule WHERE day_of_week = 'Monday' ORDER BY schedule_time DESC;
SELECT username, email FROM user_profile WHERE gender = 'Female';
SELECT * FROM exercise_data WHERE user_id = 1 AND date >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT exercise_name, duration_minutes, calories_burned FROM exercise_data WHERE duration_minutes > 30 ORDER BY calories_burned DESC;
SELECT user_id, height_cm, weight_kg, bmi FROM health_insights WHERE bmi BETWEEN 18.5 AND 24.9;
SELECT username, email FROM user_profile WHERE gender = 'Female' ORDER BY username ASC;
SELECT app_name, platform, last_synced FROM app_integration WHERE integration_status = true AND platform = 'iOS';
